reviews.review_msg: Denise is a really nice person and she wants to see her students succeed, which is nice these days.  However, I feel like I haven't learned anything from her and am relying on what I've learned in other classes to get me by.  She is also really horrible at keeping office hours, so make sure to MAKE her know you are coming, but don't expect much.

She is amazing!!! I highly recomnad her to everyone!!! She knows her stuff and she is very passionate about what she is doing! It's inspiring to be in her class. She really listen to the students and is very supportive.
